==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Faitour
<hw>Fai"tour</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>faitor</ets> a doer, L. <ets>factor</ets>. See
<er>Factor</er>.]</ety> <def>A doer or actor; particularly, an evil
doer; a scoundrel.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Lo! <qex>faitour</qex>, there thy meed unto thee take.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fake</ent>⟦br⟧
